{"tid":1116771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE越着越短 子瑜穿極短開衩裙跳舞險走光","createTime":"2019-04-20T08:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T09:59:02.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d03718515819086d87bc97d154222167be7d0518","tid":1116771,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190420/large/1555736929_0e53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190420%2Flarge%2F1555736929_0e53.jpg&h=537cec30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜於新歌MV中穿上極短開衩裙跳舞<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190420/small/1555736950_f2b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190420%2Fsmall%2F1555736950_f2b1.jpg&h=8d0050d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民認為子瑜的造型過份性感<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190420/large/1555736952_9aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190420%2Flarge%2F1555736952_9aa5.jpg&h=4a0f7e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擔心她跳舞時會走光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國女團TWICE將於後日推出新碟《FANCY YOU》回歸樂壇，前日TWICE方面公開新歌《FANCY》的MV預告。<br />\n<br />\n近期TWICE的造型漸趨成熟性感風格，成員今次都以晒腿造型現身，當中台灣成員周子瑜就非常搶眼，她穿上極短裙跳舞，短裙旁邊更有開衩位，非常性感。不過就有網民認為子瑜的造型過份性感，擔心她跳舞時會走光，又指TWICE成員的造型「越着越短」，認為新造型不方便成員跳舞演出。"},{"pid":"fef847c306a8172bc5134c41dabc7fa305bdf6d3","tid":1116771,"uid":47135,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:22:39.000Z","msg":"不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b898799da5ac2e8aeff77e188f0c0388164d29cc","tid":1116771,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"等撚咗TWICE走性感風好耐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\